Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: US-Canada relations sour
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xsv7
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 12 Apr 1987
President Reagan visits the US's big neighbour to the north while anger rages over America's production of acid rain. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less